column1: # Table S3. Genes with antisense small RNAs enriched by FLAG::CSR-1 IP. Related to Figure 5.
# 5574 genes with at least 10 small RNA reads per million and enriched at least two-fold in the FLAG::CSR-1 IP over the Input sample.
# FLAG::CSR-1 IP RPM = FLAG::CSR-1 IP RPM normalized to the total number of genome-matching reads
# Input RPM = Input RPM normalized to the total number of genome-matching reads
# IP Enrichment = Enrichment of small RNA reads in the FLAG::CSR-1 IP relative to the Input (FLAG::CSR-1 IP RPM)/(FLAG::CSR-1 RPM +Input RPM)
